S\n| score = 41\u201346\n| attend = 101,821\n}}\n|{{CFB schedule entry\n| date = November 16\n| time = 11:00 a.m.\n| w/l = w\n| away = yes\n| rank = 5\n| opponent = [[2019 Mississippi State Bulldogs football team|Mississippi State]]\n| site_stadium = [[Davis Wade Stadium]]\n| site_cityst = [[Starkville, Mississippi|Starkville, MS]]\n| gamename = [[Alabama\u2013Mississippi State football rivalry|rivalry]]\n| tv = ESPN\n| score = 38\u20137\n| attend = 57,607\n}}\n|{{CFB schedule entry\n| date = November 23\n| time = 11:00 a.m.\n| w/l = w\n| rank = 5\n| nonconf = yes\n| opponent = [[2019 Western Carolina Catamounts football team|Western Carolina]]\n| site_stadium = Bryant\u2013Denny Stadium\n| site_cityst = Tuscaloosa, AL\n| tv = ESPN\n| score = 66\u20133\n| attend = 101,821\n}}\n|{{CFB schedule entry\n| date = November 30\n| time = 2:30 p.m.\n| w/l = l\n| rank = 5\n| away = yes\n| opponent = [[2019 Auburn Tigers football team|Auburn]]\n| opprank = 15\n| site_stadium = [[Jordan\u2013Hare Stadium]]\n| site_cityst = [[Auburn, Alabama|Auburn, AL]]\n| gamename = [[Alabama\u2013Auburn football rivalry|Iron Bowl]]\n| tv = CBS\n| score = 45\u201348\n| attend = 87,451\n}}\n|{{CFB schedule entry\n| date = {{tooltip|January 1, 2020|Wednesday}}\n| time = 12:00 p.m.\n| w/l = w\n| rank = 13\n| nonconf = yes\n| neutral = yes\n| opponent = [[2019 Michigan Wolverines football team|Michigan]]\n| opprank = 14\n| site_stadium = [[Camping World Stadium]]\n| site_cityst = [[Orlando, Florida|Orlando, FL]]\n| gamename = [[2020 Citrus Bowl|Citrus Bowl]]\n| tv = ABC\n| score = 35\u201316\n| attend = 59,746\n}}\n}}\n:'''Schedule Source:'''<ref>{{cite web |title=2019 Alabama Crimson Tide Football Schedule|url=https://fbschedules.com/ncaa-2019/team/alabamalabama|publisher=FB Schedules|accessdate=January 3, 2019}}</ref>\n\n==Coaching staff==\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"font-size:90%;\"\n|-\n! style=\"background:#A32638;\" |<span style=\"color:white;\">Name</span>\n! style=\"background:#A32638;