42\n|Home='''Alabama'''\n|H1=101\n|H2=127\n|H3=107\n|H4=54\n}}\n|}\n\n==Awards and honors==\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"width: 90%;text-align: center;\"\n|+ style={{CollegePrimaryStyle|Alabama Crimson Tide}} | Weekly Awards\n!style={{CollegePrimaryStyle|Alabama Crimson Tide}} | Player\n!style={{CollegePrimaryStyle|Alabama Crimson Tide}} | Position\n!style={{CollegePrimaryStyle|Alabama Crimson Tide}} | Date\n!style={{CollegePrimaryStyle|Alabama Crimson Tide}} | Ref.\n|- align=\"center\"\n| Tua Tagovailoa (Co-SEC Offensive Player of the Week)\n| QB\n| September 2, 2019\n| <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.secsports.com/article/27521754/football-players-week|title=Week 1: Football Players of the Week|publisher=secsports.com|author=SEC Staff|date=September 2, 2019|accessdate=September 2, 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n| D.J. Dale (Co-SEC Defensive Lineman Player of the Week)\n| DL\n| September 2, 2019\n|\n|-\n| Tua Tagovailoa (2), (SEC Offensive Player of the Week)\n| QB\n| September 16, 2019\n| <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.secsports.com/article/27630099/football-players-week|title=Week 3: Football Players of the Week|publisher=secsports.com|author=SEC Staff|date=September 16, 2019|accessdate=September 16, 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n| Landon Dickerson (SEC Offensive Lineman Player of the Week)\n| OL\n| September 16, 2019\n|\n|-\n| DeVonta Smith (SEC Offensive Player of the Week)\n| WR\n| September 30, 2019\n| <ref>{{cite web|url= https://www.secsports.com/article/27736178/football-players-week|title= Week 5: Football Players of the Week |publisher=secsports.com|author=SEC Staff|date=September 30, 2019|accessdate=September 30, 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n| Jaylen Waddle (SEC Special Teams Player of the Week)\n| WR/PR\n| October 14, 2019\n| <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.secsports.com/article/27844481/football-players-week|title=Week 7: Football Players of the Week|date=October 14, 2019|website=SECSports.com|publisher=Southeastern Conference}}</ref>\n|-\n| Alex Leatherwood (SEC Offensive Lineman